trans_title: 邱瑞秋的厨房笔记：伦敦
introduction: In her new television adventure, Rachel bids au revoir to her Parisian stopping grounds, and heads back to her hometown of London. ‘Rachel Khoo’s Kitchen Notebook: London’ is a vibrant, creative and dynamic tour of London, and in 10 episodes Rachel shares the colours, sights and sounds (and food!) that inspire her in the bustling capital. Aimed at a global audience and airing around the world, the series launched in Poland on January 6, 2014.  ‘Rachel Khoo’s Kitchen Notebook: London’ is currently airing via the following BBC territories: BBC Poland, BBC Nordic, BBC Middle East, BBC Asia, and BBC South Africa.(fromhttp://www.rachelkhoo.com/tv)
